addFeed(address).details: Adds a new feed to be part of eETH's calculations.

params.newFeed_: represents a new asset fo eETH's price action.

changeUniPool(address).details: Changes the Uniswap pool used as TWAP oracle.

changeVolatilityIndex(address).details: Changes Chainlink's feed in charge of the volatility index.

getEnergyPrice().details: It aggregates the net price differences of WTI and Gold in function of basePrice's ratio and adds it to basePrice itself.

getPriceFeeds().details: Gets all the feeds use in eETH's calculations.

getTwapEth().details: Gets Uniswap's TWAP Spot Oracle price.

getVolatilityIndex().details: Gets Chainlink's volatility index to be used to amplify the price different of each asset feed (WTI and Gold).

removeFeed(address).details: Removes a feed from eETH's calculations.

params.toRemove_: asset feed that will be removed.

getEnergyPrice().notice: Gets the price in USD of Energy-ETH.
